data.title: 2012) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: In the last years of her life, Lottie always said that she was born in 1923.  In the earlier part of her life, many of us thought that she was born in 1920.  Census records of 1920 show that she was alive, so obviously, she was three years older, than she said that she was.  LOL  When having her grave marker made, we...
